  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of LX9211 in Patients With Postherpetic Neuralgia</brief_title>
  <acronym>RELIEF-PHN1</acronym>
  <official_title>A Phase 2, Double-blind, Randomized, Placebo-controlled, Parallel-group Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of LX9211 in the Treatment of Postherpetic Neuralgia (RELIEF-PHN1)</official_title>
